<HEADLINE> Honduran Foreign Debt To Diminish </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Honduras is to benefit the reduction of its debt in a term of
10 to 11 years, within the Highly Indebted Poor Countries (HIPC)
project.
</P>
<P>
The IMF approved last week the program of relief for Honduras
and it is foreseen that the World Bank (WB) will do the same on
Thursday. Both organizations declared this country eligible to
enter the HIPC.
