exchange views on regional and international issues of common
concern in Shanghai, China, in April 1996. And the annual summit
mechanism of the five nations is thereafter referred to as the "
Shanghai Five."
</P>
<P>
"I welcome you to attend the 'Shanghai Five' meeting," Jiang
said to Karimov, noting that Uzebekistan is a country of important
influence in the central Asian region.
</P>
<P>
