constituencies as Bindura, Chinhoyi, Marondera East, Mberengwa
East and West, Chengutu and Masvingo South.
</P>
<P>
Most of the contested constituencies were tightly contested
with candidates of the ruling Zimbabwe African National
Union-Patriotic Front (ZANU-PF) beating the MDC candidates by
narrow margins.
