<HEADLINE> India Supports Restoration of Peace in Sri Lanka: FM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
This was conveyed by Indian External Affairs Minister Jaswant
Singh during his meeting with Lakshman Jayakody, special envoy of
Sri Lankan President Chandrika Kumaratunga who is here on a three-
day visit, an Indian foreign office spokesman said on Wednesday.
</P>
