<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, July 5 (Xinhua) -- Grant Hill confirmed that he was
to sign with the Orlando Magic next season and wished his old team
of Detroit Pistons well.
</P>
<P>
"I'm leaning toward signing with Orlando, it's not 100 percent,
but it's close," said Hill. "This is just a golden opportunity,
for basketball reasons."
</P>
<P>
