the NBA. He shot 48.9 percent from the field and 79.5 percent from
the free throw line. He averaged 6.6 rebounds and 5.2 assists.
</P>
<P>
The Magic are offering Hill and San Antonio free agent forward
Tim Duncan six-year deals worth 67.5 million US dollars, the most
allowed under the collective bargaining agreement. 
