<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, July 5 (Xinhua) -- Twice U.S. Open champion Pat Rafter
was the first to reach last four by powering to a 6-3, 6-2, 7-6
triumph over 114th-ranked German Alexander Popp on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
