<HEADLINE> Company of HK Garrison Cited (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 5 (Xinhua) -- Jiang Zemin, chairman of the
Central Military Commission, has signed a decree to reward a
company of the Hong Kong Garrison of the Chinese People's
Liberation Army (PLA).
</P>
<P>
The No.2 Company of the No.1 Battalion of the PLA barracks in
the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR) has been granted
the title of "Model Red No.2 Company of the Hong Kong Garrison."
</P>
