driving below the rostrum around 21:00 January 15 to Chang'an
Avenue.
</P>
<P>
At the north end of Golden Water Bridge, it damaged the four-
meter-high white marble columns on both sides of the bridge, as
well as over a dozen stone slabs, which are of great historical
value.
</P>
<P>
The defendant was arrested on the spot by police.
</P>
<P>
Experts said that the accident has caused an irreparable loss
to the historic relics of the Golden Water Bridge. 
