<HEADLINE> Israel Urges Lebanon to Deploy Troops in South </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, July 5 (xinhua) -- Israeli Deputy Defense Minister
Ephraim Sneh on Wednesday attacked the Lebanese government for its
delay in redeploying its troops in south Lebanon.
</P>
<P>
