On June 9, relatives of the kidnapped man sent the money, but
the kidnappers added another three million Hong Kong dollars to
the original sum, saying they would kill their hostage if the
money did not appear.
</P>
<P>
At that point, Shantou police assigned a dozen officers to
closely monitor the activities of Chen Shaoping, Huang's wife. On
June 12 the police freed the kidnapped businessman and detained
Chen who was trying to flee with three million Hong Kong dollars.
</P>
<P>
Police said they are still pursuing other members of the
criminal gang. 
