<HEADLINE> Three Quakes Rock Northernmost Philippines </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, July 5 (Xinhua) -- Residents of the northernmost
Philippine province of Batanes experienced three continuous
earthquakes Wednesday,the Philippine Institute of Volcanology and
Seismology (Philvocs) said.
</P>
