will carry out strategic adjustment in economic structure,
implement all-around exploitation in China's western areas,
further put into effect the strategies of nation-building through
technology, education and sustainable development, continue in-
depth reforms in the economic system, and speed up the pace of the
opening-up process.
</P>
<P>
In the first decade of the new century, Chinese economy will
surely see greater and better development, and will have closer
ties with the world economy, Zhu said.
